#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:855
msgid ""
"<b>Enable dark theme:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the system theme is asked to use a darker styling for the "
"application <i>(i.e. dark UI elements on bright text)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Note that not all system themes provide such a darker variant, therefore "
"enabling this setting might not have an effect."
msgstr ""
"<b>Omogoči temno temo:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, mora sistemska tema uporabiti temnejši slog za aplikacijo <i>(tj. temni elementi uporabniškega vmesnika na svetlem besedilu)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Upoštevajte, da vse sistemske teme ne ponujajo tako temnejše različice, zato omogočanje te nastavitve morda ne bo imelo učinka."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:873
msgid ""
"<b>Enable client-side decorations:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search entry and main menu are displayed in the window title "
"bar.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the main menu is displayed as a menu bar with the search entry "
"below it.\n"
"This resembles a more traditional UI layout and takes a little bit more "
"space."
msgstr ""
"<b>Omogoči okraske na strani odjemalca:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, sta iskalni vnos in glavni meni prikazana v naslovni vrstici okna.\n"
"\n"
"Če je onemogočen, je glavni meni prikazan kot menijska vrstica z iskalnim vnosom pod njim.\n"
"To spominja na bolj tradicionalno postavitev uporabniškega vmesnika in zavzame malo več prostora."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:893
msgid ""
"<b>Use binary units instead of decimal units:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This settings controls how file sizes are displayed.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Binary units:</b> This refers to binary IEC prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 KiB = "
"1024 bytes)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Decimal  units:</b> This refers to decimal SI prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 kB "
"= 1000 bytes)</i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Uporabite binarne enote namesto decimalnih enot:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ta nastavitev nadzira, kako so prikazane velikosti datotek.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Binarne enote:</b> To se nanaša na binarne predpone IEC <i>(npr. 1 KiB = 1024 bajtov)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Decimalne enote:</b> To se nanaša na decimalne predpone SI <i>(npr. 1 kB = 1000 bajtov)</i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:913
msgid ""
"<b>Remember window size:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the window size from the previous session will be restored when "
"you open an FSearch window.\n"
"\n"
"Note that some window managers ignore this request and force the window to "
"have a different size."
msgstr ""
"<b>Zapomni si velikost okna:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bo velikost okna iz prejšnje seje obnovljena, ko odprete okno FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Upoštevajte, da nekateri upravitelji oken ignorirajo to zahtevo in vsilijo, da ima okno drugačno velikost."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:932
msgid ""
"<b>Behaviour after successfully opening a file:</b>\n"
"\n"
"When a file/folder was successfully opened one of the following actions can "
"be performed:\n"
"\t• <b>Nothing:</b> Nothing happens.\n"
"                        • <b>Minimize:</b> The currently selected FSearch "
"window becomes minimized.\n"
"\t• <b>Close:</b> Quit FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"You can configure if those actions should be triggered when the file was "
"opened with\n"
"\t• <b>keyboard shortcuts or menu entries</b> and/or\n"
"\t• <b>mouse click</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Vedenje po uspešnem odprtju datoteke:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ko je bila datoteka/mapa uspešno odprta, je mogoče izvesti eno od naslednjih dejanj:\n"
"\t• <b>Nič:</b> Nič se ne zgodi.\n"
"                        • <b>Pomanjšaj:</b> Trenutno izbrano okno FSearch postane pomanjšano.\n"
"\t• <b>Zapri:</b> Zapustite FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Konfigurirate lahko, ali naj se ta dejanja sprožijo, ko je bila datoteka odprta z\n"
"\t• <b>bližnjice na tipkovnici ali vnosi v meni</b> in/ali\n"
"\t• <b>klik z miško</b>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:956
msgid ""
"<b>Show highlighted search terms:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search terms will be highlighted in the results view. For "
"example when you search for \"foo\" all appearances of <i>foo</i> in file/"
"folder names will be highlighted with bold characters:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfile.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"This also works for regular expressions and wildcard expressions starting or "
"ending with an asterisk. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Pokaži označene iskalne izraze:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bodo iskalni izrazi označeni v pogledu rezultatov. Ko na primer iščete \\\"foo\\\", bodo vsi pojavi <i>foo</i> v imenih datotek/map označeni s krepkimi znaki:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tdatoteka.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"To deluje tudi za regularne izraze in izraze z nadomestnimi znaki, ki se začnejo ali končajo z zvezdico."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:978
msgid ""
"<b>Show tooltips:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the results view will show the full path of the focused file/"
"folder in a small tooltip window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Pokaži nasvete orodij:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bo pogled rezultatov prikazal celotno pot izbrane datoteke/mape v majhnem oknu z opisom orodja."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:995
msgid ""
"<b>Show icons in name column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, file/folder icons will be shown in the name column."
msgstr ""
"<b>Pokaži ikone v stolpcu imena:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bodo ikone datotek/map prikazane v stolpcu z imenom."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1012
msgid ""
"<b>Remember column configuration:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the column configuration of the results view from the previous "
"session will be restored when you open an FSearch window. This includes the "
"size and visibility of all columns."
msgstr ""
"<b>Zapomni si konfiguracijo stolpcev:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bo konfiguracija stolpcev pogleda rezultatov iz prejšnje seje obnovljena, ko odprete okno FSearch. To vključuje velikost in vidnost vseh stolpcev."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1029
msgid ""
"<b>Remember sort order:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the sort order of the results view from the previous session "
"will be restored when you open an FSearch window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Zapomni si vrstni red razvrščanja:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bo vrstni red pogleda rezultatov iz prejšnje seje obnovljen, ko odprete okno FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1046
msgid ""
"<b>Open path with double click in path column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, double clicking in the path column will open the selected path."
msgstr ""
"<b>Odprite pot z dvoklikom v stolpcu poti:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bo dvojni klik v stolpcu poti odprl izbrano pot."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1063
msgid ""
"<b>Single click to open:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a single click will open the selected file/folder. If you only "
"want to select a file/folder while this setting is active, you need to hold "
"<i>Ctrl</i> at the same time while clicking the file/folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>En klik za odpiranje:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bo izbrana datoteka/mapa odprta z enim klikom. Če želite izbrati samo datoteko/mapo, medtem ko je ta nastavitev aktivna, morate istočasno držati <i>Ctrl</i>, medtem ko kliknete datoteko/mapo."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1080
msgid ""
"<b>Show database indexing status:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the path that is currently being indexed is displayed in the "
"statusbar."
msgstr ""
"<b>Pokaži stanje indeksiranja zbirke podatkov:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, je pot, ki se trenutno indeksira, prikazana v vrstici stanja."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1097
msgid ""
"<b>Show warning dialogs:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a warning dialog is displayed when a file or folder failed to "
"open."
msgstr ""
"<b>Pokaži opozorilna pogovorna okna:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, se prikaže opozorilno pogovorno okno, ko se datoteka ali mapa ne odpre."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1114
msgid ""
"<b>Search in path when query contains path separators:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing path separators (i.e. \"/\") will be "
"automatically matched against the full path of a file or folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Išči po poti, ko poizvedba vsebuje ločila poti:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bodo iskalni izrazi, ki vsebujejo ločila poti (tj. \\\"/\\\"), samodejno primerjani s celotno potjo datoteke ali mape."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1131
msgid ""
"<b>Match case when query contains at least one upper case character:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing at least one upper case character will "
"trigger a case-sensitive search. This means a search term like <i>Foo</i> "
"will match <i>FooBar.txt</i> but not <i>foobar.txt</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ujemanje velikih črk, ko poizvedba vsebuje vsaj eno veliko črko:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bodo iskalni izrazi, ki vsebujejo vsaj eno veliko črko, sprožili iskanje, ki razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami. To pomeni, da se bo iskalni izraz, kot je <i>Foo</i>, ujemal z <i>FooBar.txt</i>, ne pa tudi z <i>foobar.txt</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1148
msgid ""
"<b>Hide results when search is empty:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, no search results are displayed when the search entry is empty.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, all files and folders will be displayed when the search entry "
"is empty."
msgstr ""
"<b>Skrij rezultate, ko je iskanje prazno:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, rezultati iskanja niso prikazani, ko je iskalni vnos prazen.\n"
"\n"
"Če je onemogočeno, bodo vse datoteke in mape prikazane, ko bo iskalni vnos prazen."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1167
msgid ""
"<b>Search as you type:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search is automatically updated with every keystroke.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the search is only updated when you hit <i>Enter</i> or press "
"the search button. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Išči med tipkanjem:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, se iskanje samodejno posodobi z vsakim pritiskom na tipko.\n"
"\n"
"Če je onemogočeno, se iskanje posodobi šele, ko pritisnete <i>Enter</i> ali pritisnete gumb za iskanje."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1186
msgid ""
"<b>Update database on start:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the database will be updated automatically in the background "
"when you start FSearch."
msgstr ""
"<b>Posodobi bazo podatkov ob začetku:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, se baza podatkov samodejno posodobi v ozadju, ko zaženete FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1203
msgid ""
"<b>Included folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains all folders you want to include in the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the path will included in the database to be "
"searched in.\n"
"\t• <b>Path:</b> The full path to be included.\n"
"\t• <b>One Filesystem:</b> If enabled, FSearch won't cross filesystem "
"boundaries for this folder"
msgstr ""
"<b>Vključene mape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ta seznam vsebuje vse mape, ki jih želite vključiti v bazo podatkov.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Aktivno:</b> Če je omogočeno, bo pot vključena v zbirko podatkov, v kateri se bo iskalo.\n"
"\t• <b>Pot:</b> Celotna pot, ki bo vključena.\n"
"\t• <b>En datotečni sistem:</b> če je omogočen, FSearch ne bo prestopil meja datotečnega sistema za to mapo"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1224
msgid ""
"<b>Add folder to database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can select a folder you want to include "
"in the database for searching."
msgstr ""
"<b>Dodaj mapo v bazo podatkov:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno, kjer lahko izberete mapo, ki jo želite vključiti v zbirko podatkov za iskanje."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1241
msgid ""
"<b>Add a specific path:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Type the full path of a folder here and click the button next to it to "
"include that folder in the database. This is useful for adding a path "
"directly without browsing for it."
msgstr ""
"<b>Dodajte določeno pot:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Tukaj vnesite celotno pot do mape in kliknite gumb poleg nje, da to mapo vključite v bazo podatkov. To je uporabno za neposredno dodajanje poti brez brskanja po njej."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1258
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected folder from the list of included folders."
msgstr ""
"<b>Odstrani izbrano vrstico:</b>\n"
"\n"
"S tem odstranite izbrano mapo s seznama vključenih map."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1275
msgid ""
"<b>Attempt to monitor:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch watches this folder for changes and keeps the database "
"up to date automatically, so you don't have to rescan manually.\n"
"\n"
"Monitoring isn't supported on every file system and uses a small amount of "
"system resources per watched folder. For large directory trees with many "
"files the system may run out of resources to watch them all."
msgstr ""
"<b>Poskusi nadzora:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, FSearch opazuje to mapo za spremembe in samodejno posodablja zbirko podatkov, tako da vam ni treba znova ročno skenirati.\n"
"\n"
"Spremljanje ni podprto v vseh datotečnih sistemih in uporablja majhno količino sistemskih virov na opazovano mapo. Pri velikih imeniških drevesih z veliko datotekami lahko sistemu zmanjka sredstev za ogled vseh."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1294
msgid ""
"<b>Scan after launch:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned every time FSearch starts, so the "
"database reflects any changes made while FSearch wasn't running."
msgstr ""
"<b>Skeniraj po zagonu:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, se ta mapa znova pregleda vsakič, ko se FSearch zažene, tako da zbirka podatkov odraža vse spremembe, ki so bile narejene, ko FSearch ni deloval."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1311
msgid ""
"<b>Stay on one file system:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch won't cross file system boundaries while scanning this "
"folder. Mounted file systems below it (e.g. external drives or network "
"shares) are skipped."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ostanite na enem datotečnem sistemu:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, FSearch med skeniranjem te mape ne bo prestopil meja datotečnega sistema. Nameščeni datotečni sistemi pod njim (npr. zunanji diski ali omrežni deli) so preskočeni."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1328
msgid ""
"<b>Rescan every:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned automatically at the given interval. "
"Use the hours and minutes fields to set how often the rescan happens.\n"
"\n"
"This is useful for folders on file systems that can't be monitored for "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ponovno skeniraj vsak:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, se ta mapa samodejno ponovno pregleda v danem intervalu. Uporabite polja za ure in minute, da nastavite, kako pogosto se ponovi pregled.\n"
"\n"
"To je uporabno za mape v datotečnih sistemih, ki jih ni mogoče spremljati glede sprememb."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1347
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains rules for the files and folders you want to exclude from "
"the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the rule is applied and matching items are "
"excluded.\n"
"\t• <b>Pattern:</b> The text matched against each item, interpreted "
"according to the Type.\n"
"\t• <b>Type:</b> How the pattern is interpreted — <i>Literal</i> (exact "
"text), <i>Wildcard</i> (using * and ?) or <i>Regex</i> (a regular "
"expression).\n"
"\t• <b>Match:</b> Whether the pattern is matched against the item's <i>Full "
"Path</i> or only its <i>Basename</i> (the name without the path).\n"
"\t• <b>Applies To:</b> Whether the rule affects <i>Files</i>, <i>Folders</i> "
"or both."
msgstr ""
"<b>Izključi pravila:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ta seznam vsebuje pravila za datoteke in mape, ki jih želite izključiti iz zbirke podatkov.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Aktivno:</b> Če je omogočeno, se pravilo uporabi in ujemajoči se elementi so izključeni.\n"
"\t• <b>Vzorec:</b> Besedilo se ujema z vsakim elementom, interpretirano glede na vrsto.\n"
"\t• <b>Tip:</b> Kako se vzorec interpretira — <i>Literal</i> (natančno besedilo), <i>Nadomestni znak</i> (z * in?) ali <i>Regex</i> (regularni izraz).\n"
"\t• <b>Ujemanje:</b> ali se vzorec ujema s <i>celotno potjo</i> predmeta ali samo z njegovim <i>osnovnim imenom</i> (ime brez poti).\n"
"\t• <b>Velja za:</b> Ali pravilo vpliva na <i>Datoteke</i>, <i>Mape</i> ali oboje."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1370
msgid ""
"<b>Add exclude rule:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This adds a new, empty rule to the list. Edit its Pattern, Type, Match and "
"Applies To columns to control what gets excluded from the database."
msgstr ""
"<b>Dodaj pravilo za izključitev:</b>\n"
"\n"
"To na seznam doda novo, prazno pravilo. Uredite njegove stolpce Vzorec, Vrsta, Ujemanje in Velja za, da nadzirate, kaj bo izključeno iz zbirke podatkov."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1387
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected rule from the list of exclude rules."
msgstr ""
"<b>Odstrani izbrano vrstico:</b>\n"
"\n"
"S tem odstranite izbrano pravilo s seznama izključenih pravil."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1404
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default set of exclude rules.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All rules which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Obnovi privzeta pravila za izključitev:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ta gumb obnovi privzeti nabor pravil za izključitev.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Vsa pravila, ki jih je ustvaril ali uredil uporabnik, bodo izgubljena! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1423
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude files and folders from database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a semi-colon separated list of files (or folders) you want to "
"exclude from the database. For example <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> will exclude "
"all files or folders which are called either <i>.git</i> or <i>.cache</i> or "
"end with <i>.swp</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Izključi datoteke in mape iz zbirke podatkov:</b>\n"
"\n"
"To je s podpičjem ločen seznam datotek (ali map), ki jih želite izključiti iz zbirke podatkov. Na primer <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> bo izključil vse datoteke ali mape, ki se imenujejo <i>.git</i> ali <i>.cache</i> ali se končajo z <i>.swp</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1440
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude hidden files and folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, hidden files and folders will be excluded from the database "
"<i>(i.e. all files or folders which start with a dot character)</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Izključi skrite datoteke in mape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bodo skrite datoteke in mape izključene iz zbirke podatkov <i>(tj. vse datoteke ali mape, ki se začnejo s piko)</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1457
msgid "Focus a setting to get a detailed description of what it does."
msgstr "Osredotočite se na nastavitev, da dobite podroben opis, kaj počne."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1470
msgid ""
"<b>Periodically update database at a specific time interval:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled and as long as FSearch is running, the database will be updated "
"periodically with the given time interval.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to update the database in the background, even when FSearch is "
"not running, you should use tools like cron or systemd timers to "
"periodically trigger the update with:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Občasno posodabljajte bazo podatkov v določenem časovnem intervalu:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno in dokler FSearch deluje, se bo zbirka podatkov redno posodabljala v danem časovnem intervalu.\n"
"\n"
"Če želite bazo podatkov posodobiti v ozadju, tudi ko FSearch ni zagnan, uporabite orodja, kot sta časovniki cron ali systemd, da občasno sprožite posodobitev z:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1491
msgid ""
"<b>Launch desktop files:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, activating a <i>.desktop</i> file will launch the application "
"defined within that file. This way FSearch can act like an application "
"launcher. Otherwise the <i>.desktop</i> file will be opened with the default "
"handler for this type of files, which is usually a text editor."
msgstr ""
"<b>Zagon namiznih datotek:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, bo aktiviranje datoteke <i>.desktop</i> zagnalo aplikacijo, definirano v tej datoteki. Tako lahko FSearch deluje kot zaganjalnik aplikacij. V nasprotnem primeru bo datoteka <i>.desktop</i> odprta s privzetim upravljalnikom za to vrsto datotek, ki je običajno urejevalnik besedil."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1508
msgid ""
"<b>Filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a list of all available filters. A filter is a predefined search.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Name:</b> A unique and descriptive identifier for the filter\n"
"\t• <b>Macro:</b> By typing the macro text followed by a ':' you can enable "
"the filter on demand\n"
"\t• <b>Query:</b> The search term by which the database should be filtered"
msgstr ""
"<b>Filtri:</b>\n"
"\n"
"To je seznam vseh razpoložljivih filtrov. Filter je vnaprej določeno iskanje.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Ime:</b> edinstven in opisni identifikator filtra\n"
"\t• <b>Makro:</b> Če vnesete besedilo makra, ki mu sledi ':', lahko omogočite filter na zahtevo\n"
"\t• <b>Poizvedba:</b> Iskalni izraz, po katerem naj bo podatkovna baza filtrirana"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1529
msgid ""
"<b>Add a new filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit a new filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Dodajte nov filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno, kjer lahko uredite nov filter."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1546
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button removes the currently selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Odstrani izbrani filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ta gumb odstrani trenutno izbrani filter."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1563
msgid ""
"<b>Edit selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit the selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Urejanje izbranega filtra:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno, kjer lahko uredite izbrani filter."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1580
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default filter configuration.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All filters which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Obnovi privzete filtre:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ta gumb obnovi privzeto konfiguracijo filtra.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Vsi filtri, ki jih je ustvaril ali uredil uporabnik, bodo izgubljeni! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1599
msgid ""
"<b>Exit on Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch exits when the Escape key is pressed instead of the "
"window being minimized."
msgstr ""
"<b>Izhod na Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, se FSearch zapre, ko pritisnete tipko Escape, namesto da se okno pomanjša."

